{"tid":2432991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國統計發現接種第二劑出現輕微副作用較接種第一劑後高","createTime":"2021-03-04T16:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T16:20:35.000Z","uid":39206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2772d7abbf00d12ee9aa2e7e8b8076f90be89ac","tid":2432991,"uid":39206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T16:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1AryU9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1AryU9.jpg&h=21c3050a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在美國，最常見的輕微副作用是針口痛，接種首劑後近百萬人有68人有此情況；第二劑增至近百萬人中75人有此情況。另外，接種首劑後近百萬人有7人顫抖；第二劑增加近3倍至27人。現時美國主要安排國民接種輝瑞/BioNTech和莫德納兩款mRNA疫苗；科學雜誌《自然》引述數據時指出，出現副作用情況比臨床測試數字少。"},{"pid":"cc7e7e5e48cf229437a5064351748906f1d95845","tid":2432991,"uid":39206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"祖國疫苗冇呢個問題<br />\n因為打完就即刻歸西<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a617f846859cabb455b7e355880d3944d0496f","tid":2432991,"uid":91454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"某國<br />\n廢:我打完點針口痛啊，洗唔洗mark低？<br />\n某:屌你打針緊係會痛，mark乜撚野啊"}],"pinned":{"pid":"cc7e7e5e48cf229437a5064351748906f1d95845","tid":2432991,"uid":39206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"祖國疫苗冇呢個問題<br />\n因為打完就即刻歸西<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}